Global Water Surface Photovoltaic System Market Insights
Water Surface Photovoltaic System Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 18.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Water Surface Photovoltaic System Market Overview
The Water Surface Photovoltaic (WSPV) system market is projected to reach a market value of $12.5 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 19.3% from 2023. The increasing demand for renewable energy sources, the depletion of land resources for solar installations, and the technological advancements in floating solar panels are driving market growth. The WSPV systems are increasingly being deployed in regions with abundant water bodies and high solar irradiance, offering an efficient way to harness solar energy. The market's development is also fueled by global environmental sustainability initiatives, promoting the reduction of carbon footprints.

